    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "He built even Bethlehem,.... The place of our Lord's birth, about six miles from Jerusalem: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and Etam; another city in the tribe of Judah; see 1 Chronicles 4:32, there was a rock of this name, Judges 15:8 and a fountain from whence waters were conveyed into the pool at Jerusalem, spoken of in Jewish writings (b): ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and Etam; another city in the tribe of Judah; see ",
            "children": []
